<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 18:41:19 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>圣海伦</title><link>https://some.pics/6a455f4b5cd1e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从天空俯瞰圣海伦斯火山。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Photo of Mount St Helens at the cloud line, taken from an airplane." height="3072" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ballpointcarrot/6a455f4b5cd1e.jpg" width="4096"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ballpointcarrot.some.pics"&gt;@ballpointcarrot&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 18:41:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a45575a0a294</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊克&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Icke" height="2522" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/b30/6a45575a0a294.png" width="2316"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://b30.some.pics"&gt;@b30&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 18:07:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>微微脸红</title><link>https://some.pics/6a44e4cda9541</link><description>&lt;p&gt;略微脸红&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A red currant that is already slightly red on one side." height="2978" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a44e4cda9541.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 09:58:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>社区入口壁画成地标</title><link>https://some.pics/6a44ca517d988</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在历史悠久的英格赛德社区入口处，艾琳·霍金斯创作的这幅异想天开的壁画是那些让人忍不住驻足微笑的细节之一。这幅色彩缤纷的艺术品迅速成为当地备受喜爱的地标，既让居民感到自豪，也为游客提供了一个有趣的驻足拍照地点。这不仅仅是一件美丽的艺术作品，壁画还为社区增添了独特个性，展现了创造力、魅力和热情好客的精神，正是这些特质让英格赛德成为一个如此特别的地方。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A colorful mural on a brick wall reads “Ingleside Macon, GA” in large blue lettering, surrounded by white clouds and small painted birds. The mural sits on the side of a building under a clear blue sky." height="2913" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a44ca517d988.jpg" width="3884"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 08:05:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a448ae104c95</link><description>&lt;p&gt;人和高尔夫球车火车桥&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A paved path leads under a rustic bridge surrounded by dense green foliage, opening into a bright grassy field beyond." height="3425" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a448ae104c95.jpg" width="4567"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 03:35:01 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>